    <item>
      <title>Overview</title>
      <link>http://localhost:45189/docs/packaging/recipes/system-accounts/overview/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:45189/docs/packaging/recipes/system-accounts/overview/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;As a stateless distribution, AerynOS does not permit the modification of &lt;code&gt;/etc/passwd&lt;/code&gt; and co by packages or triggers. Instead, we integrate &lt;code&gt;nss-systemd&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;userdb&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hx:overflow-x-auto hx:mt-6 hx:flex hx:rounded-lg hx:border hx:py-2 hx:ltr:pr-4 hx:rtl:pl-4 hx:contrast-more:border-current hx:contrast-more:dark:border-current hx:border-amber-200 hx:bg-amber-100 hx:text-amber-900 hx:dark:border-amber-200/30 hx:dark:bg-amber-900/30 hx:dark:text-amber-200&#34;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;hx:ltr:pl-3 hx:ltr:pr-2 hx:rtl:pr-3 hx:rtl:pl-2&#34;&gt;&lt;svg height=1.2em class=&#34;hx:inline-block hx:align-middle&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;path stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; d=&#34;M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

  &lt;div class=&#34;hx:w-full hx:min-w-0 hx:leading-7&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hx:mt-6 hx:leading-7 hx:first:mt-0&#34;&gt;The use of &lt;code&gt;nss&lt;/code&gt; means that user accounts and groups defined by this mechanism are only available to packages using the correct &lt;code&gt;glibc&lt;/code&gt; APIs. Statically linking with &lt;code&gt;musl&lt;/code&gt; or directly reading &lt;code&gt;/etc/passwd&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;/etc/group&lt;/code&gt;, etc, will not reveal these accounts.&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The main benefit with this approach is ensuring that we do not directly mutate system files, and that unlike the &lt;code&gt;sysusers&lt;/code&gt; mechanism, removal of a package ensures these system user and group definitions are no longer available.&lt;/p&gt;

      </description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Groups</title>
      <link>http://localhost:45189/docs/packaging/recipes/system-accounts/groups/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:45189/docs/packaging/recipes/system-accounts/groups/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;Refer to the &lt;a href=&#34;https://systemd.io/GROUP_RECORD/&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;JSON Group Record&lt;svg class=&#34;hx:inline hx:rtl:rotate-270 hx:align-baseline&#34; height=&#34;1em&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;&gt;
 &lt;path d=&#34;m9.1716 7.7574h7.0711m0 0v7.0711m0-7.0711-8.4853 8.4853&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;/&gt;
&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt; documentation for information on all supported fields.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Example&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;example&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#example&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Within the package tree &lt;code&gt;./pkg&lt;/code&gt; add &lt;code&gt;gdm.group&lt;/code&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-json&#34; data-lang=&#34;json&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    &lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;groupName&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;gdm&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    &lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;gid&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;21&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    &lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;disposition&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;system&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Note that these are the minimum required set of fields, and &lt;code&gt;disposition&lt;/code&gt; should always be set to &lt;code&gt;system&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In your recipe&amp;rsquo;s &lt;code&gt;install&lt;/code&gt; section, you must install the file by group name &lt;em&gt;and&lt;/em&gt; by gid to the &lt;code&gt;%(libdir)/userdb&lt;/code&gt; directory:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    %install_file %&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;pkgdir&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;/gdm.group %&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;installroot&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;%&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;libdir&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;/userdb/gdm.group
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    ln -s gdm.group %&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;installroot&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;%&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;libdir&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;/userdb/21.group&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

      </description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Users</title>
      <link>http://localhost:45189/docs/packaging/recipes/system-accounts/users/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:45189/docs/packaging/recipes/system-accounts/users/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;System accounts should &lt;em&gt;always&lt;/em&gt; be marked as &lt;code&gt;locked&lt;/code&gt;. Refer to the &lt;a href=&#34;https://systemd.io/USER_RECORD/&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;JSON User Record&lt;svg class=&#34;hx:inline hx:rtl:rotate-270 hx:align-baseline&#34; height=&#34;1em&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;&gt;
 &lt;path d=&#34;m9.1716 7.7574h7.0711m0 0v7.0711m0-7.0711-8.4853 8.4853&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;/&gt;
&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt; documentation for information on all supported fields.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In AerynOS we only ship user definitions without &lt;code&gt;privileged&lt;/code&gt; or &lt;code&gt;signature&lt;/code&gt; fields.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Example&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;example&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#example&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Within the package tree &lt;code&gt;./pkg&lt;/code&gt; add &lt;code&gt;gdm.user&lt;/code&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-json&#34; data-lang=&#34;json&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    &lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;userName&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;gdm&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    &lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;realName&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;GNOME Display Manager&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    &lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;uid&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;21&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    &lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;gid&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;21&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    &lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;disposition&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;system&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    &lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;locked&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;kc&#34;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Note that these are the minimum required set of fields, and &lt;code&gt;disposition&lt;/code&gt; should always be set to &lt;code&gt;system&lt;/code&gt;. Also note that &lt;code&gt;homeDirectory&lt;/code&gt; may need setting for some packages.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In your recipe&amp;rsquo;s &lt;code&gt;install&lt;/code&gt; section, you must install the file by username &lt;em&gt;and&lt;/em&gt; by uid to the &lt;code&gt;%(libdir)/userdb&lt;/code&gt; directory:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    %install_file %&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;pkgdir&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;/gdm.user %&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;installroot&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;%&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;libdir&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;/userdb/gdm.user
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    ln -s gdm.user %&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;installroot&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;%&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;libdir&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;/userdb/21.user&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

      </description>
